Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:07.46,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway through a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:14.75,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Tears dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:22.93,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Because I closed my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:28.94,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,and distanced myself from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:35.70,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,5 PM in the school yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:42.58,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,The ball's shadow is growing tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:50.04,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:53.76,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever we meet in the hallway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:58.51,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,we always quarreled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:06.69,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway through a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.35,0:01:13.65,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,tears dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:20.99,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Because I opened my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:27.79,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,and we understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:40.28,eptitle,title,0000,0350,0000,,Episode 3\N\NWind\NTowards London.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:01:59.52,Default,girl1,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, sayonara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:00.04,Default,girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Sayonara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:01.76,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take any detours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:15.76,Default,male,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, Matsunaga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.64,Default,female,0000,0000,0000,,Why haven't you blown anything up yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:22.76,Default,male,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:28.78,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:29.68,Default,male,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:31.70,Default,chorus,0000,0000,0000,,Go see the nurse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:34.04,Default,female,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not satisfied with that little fizzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:36.06,Default,male,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not satisfied at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:42.18,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:44.54,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Ouu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:51.74,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:54.58,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:57.12,Default,Sarash,0000,0000,0000,,But there's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:02.72,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You can't put pictures like that in the grad book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:10.48,Default,Sarash,0000,0000,0000,,Here are the requests from the grads to put your pictures in the grad book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:12.98,Default,Sarash,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:18.68,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But those pictures are too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:20.58,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What's too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.74,Default,runner,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, do you hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:26.52,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!\nYou're getting on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.08,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,ehhh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:31.40,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop her, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:33.04,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:37.10,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause! She wants to put pictures like these in the grad book!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.68,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:40.54,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:43.08,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,They are good pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:44.80,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,No they are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:50.64,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,But, you're always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:51.56,Default,Sarashina,0000,0000,0000,,That is so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:52.76,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:56.22,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,If your going to use my picture, please use better pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.52,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,What pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:03:59.80,Default,Yamagi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:13.48,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:18.82,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:19.76,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:20.78,Default,Yamagi,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:38.08,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga-imouto. What is she doing here?\nI have no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:40.98,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Odd, I don't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.98,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,I should switch ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:47.86,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I hear the voice of the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.14,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.84,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:07.66,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:12.06,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to see senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:23.76,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the laugh of the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.94,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it,\nyou fell down the stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.18,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Does your back hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:37.98,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.46,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, I'll fly you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:52.20,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to walk home, do you?\nSo, I'll fly you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:56.30,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Bummer, I thought you meant London.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:58.58,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy. No way I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.22,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I should have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.08,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:25.56,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're not Mikage-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:29.90,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Matsunaga-imouto go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:36.84,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi-kun, I saw Mikage-kun enter this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.42,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,This is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.68,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:49.04,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, it's a UFO!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:50.36,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,UFO!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:51.66,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:54.76,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga-ane!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:55.50,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:07:02.02,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Wa..wa..wait a minute...\ntoo late...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:05.52,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see the UFO too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:10.04,Default,mother,0000,0000,0000,,Dear, how long will you be home this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:16.38,Default,father,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to head back to the Flentze branch in a couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:26.30,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Oww, that hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:29.80,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there? Oh, Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:32.92,Default,mother,0000,0000,0000,,Don't startle us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.62,Default,mother,0000,0000,0000,,You've done it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:41.38,Default,mother,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you not to come inside with your shoes on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:45.78,Default,mother,0000,0000,0000,,You'll leave scratches all over the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.16,Default,mother,0000,0000,0000,,Dear, you don't look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.82,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.18,Default,mother,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.28,Default,father,0000,0000,0000,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:03.56,Default,mother,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage fell down the stairs.\nShe didn't look too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.23,Default,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:07.28,Default,Kurash,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:10.16,Default,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Kurashige-san,\nyou're here to study, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:11.96,Default,Kurash,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:15.70,Default,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,My relative is ill and I'm here to look after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:24.52,Default,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,See you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.00,Default,Kurash,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:40.24,Default,father,0000,0000,0000,,It's papa. I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:46.50,Default,Mr.X,0000,0000,0000,,The sensor we just set will pick up the bio activity wave and display it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:53.72,Default,Mr.X,0000,0000,0000,,The flower's wave doesn't match with an known species of plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:54.40,Default,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:58.98,Default,Mr.X,0000,0000,0000,,There's a 99% chance its the flower of the legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:05.20,Default,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to find my younger twin sister, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.10,Default,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,My family?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:20.88,Default,OldWoman,0000,0000,0000,,I have lied whenever you asked about your family, that I was looking for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:22.36,Default,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,My family...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.40,Default,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,The people who abandoned me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:41.94,Default,OldWoman,0000,0000,0000,,However, I can't leave you behind without letting you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:20.90,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.82,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, mommy will be mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:29.60,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mi..ka...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.58,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,It's not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:26.86,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Noda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.40,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:32.28,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she went to the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:37.98,Default,Yamagi,0000,0000,0000,,Why would someone skip school to go to a library?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:40.74,Default,Yamagi,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi-chan, aren't you gonna finish that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.14,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What, Noda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:55.36,Default,Yamagi,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi-chan, are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:56.86,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:59.22,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Cause... you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:01.48,Default,Sarash,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:02.22,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:04.32,Default,Sarash,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:07.28,Default,Sarash,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring some other pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:11.34,Default,Sarash,0000,0000,0000,,The page with you is the only one not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.00,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,The page with me?...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:17.36,Default,Sarash,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I ever trust you? Silly me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:18.72,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,OH NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.24,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:26.28,Default,Sarash,0000,0000,0000,,I need them pretty quick. The printer is coming to pick them up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:28.28,Default,Sarash,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget them tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:29.24,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:13:59.16,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm not doing too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.50,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:28.02,Default,Mikage and Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,OUCH!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:35.02,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,"Noda-kun?", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.42,Default,Yamagi,0000,0000,0000,,Is something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.86,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, you're acting weird today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.44,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:51.28,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:05.70,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? I saw Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:52.00,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, what's going on? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:03.64,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen a ghost around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:10.04,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost, get it?\nTell me if you see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:11.18,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:15.38,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,She might be my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:33.10,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,The flowers seem to resonate with our power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:34.22,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Resonate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:36.40,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Our wavelengths match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:40.04,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Our wavelengths match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:46.88,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, I was thinking about the time I met senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:50.08,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:53.30,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,It was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:58.58,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to put it, but tears just kept on pouring out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:10.92,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, I think I know how much you like senpai now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.62,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I'll go see senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:21.36,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,The power of Love will beat time!\nDistance is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:25.83,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,She gets stuck on this so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:43.22,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, is the legend coming true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:44.08,Default,grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:49.86,Default,grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,The Legend of the Twin Princesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:56.14,Default,grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,Twins divided by light and shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:18:02.50,Default,grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,When the shining flowers come under the sword of light, the source of power is created...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:14.70,Default,grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,And the twins of light shall unleash their power of heaven from the flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:18.80,Default,grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,They will rain gold to make the new ruler shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:27.18,Default,grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,The new ruler shall drive all shadow from the world by the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:35.92,Default,Mr.X,0000,0000,0000,,There must be something resonating. Track the source of the other wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:39.92,Default,grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,The world will be in a state of eternal enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:05.22,Default,Kurash,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! Mikage-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:06.66,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:12.70,Default,Kurash,0000,0000,0000,,You always surprises me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:31.86,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Shuddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:34.00,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you good at sewing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:35.56,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:39.06,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:14.08,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,She sure pulls off a lot of stunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.50,Default,Mr.X,0000,0000,0000,,I almost had the source pinpointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:41.56,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you walking with a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:48.16,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,But she wasn't my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:53.54,Default,Kurash,0000,0000,0000,,She always surprise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.44,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:00.12,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.06,0:21:02.58,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:04.64,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:11.24,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Sarashina-san will be mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:13.36,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,It's got nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:17.80,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:21.12,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:25.22,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I can run for it, but you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:27.98,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:51.60,Default,M&T,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle Girls here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:54.68,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew I'd see senpai,\nI would've worn something better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:56.10,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You never had any decent ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:21:58.82,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,OK, I'll get the best one at a bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:22:01.28,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,and Tomomi, also title Next on Miracle Girls, "Bargain Typhoon."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:03.96,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you need a strategy just for a dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:08.42,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:11.91,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.99,0:22:15.03,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:18.56,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:38.55,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,There are days when kindness is so close that you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:50.44,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we know better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:58.55,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,When we can't say "I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:06.13,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:11.74,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Going over the tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:15.11,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,we want to be honest to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.53,0:23:20.90,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause the sky deserves a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:23.41,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.77,0:23:26.98,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:30.11,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:34.28,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,are better than one of us.
